snippet.title: v7.6 Fading Dreams, Dimming Shadows Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v7.6 Fading Dreams, Dimming Shadows coming soon! New S-rank battlesuit Jovial Deception: Shadowdimmer debuts!
Part 2 Main Story Chapter III Interlude: Bitterness for a Sleepwalker and featured event Schicksal Work Guide will also be available. Stay tuned!

Serapeum: Yuko Ono
Thelema: Akira Sekine

Songque: Natsumi Takamori
Dreamseeker: Yuki Nakashima
Coralie: Saya Aizawa
Helia: Yui Kondo
Senadina: Minori Suzuki
